nters, knowledgeable animal handlers, offering pet care....\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Gastonia\",\"addressRegion\":\"NC\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/avon-catawba-creeks-greenway/avon-catawba-creeks-greenway-1.jpg\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I hike with my dog near Gastonia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Crowders Mountain State Park is the jewel of the area. The trails range from moderate to strenuous, offering incredible views. Dogs must be on a leash at all times.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there a dog park in Gastonia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, the Goat Island Park (in nearby Cramerton) and Lineberger Park offer great outdoor spaces. Bradley Station Dog Park in downtown Gastonia is a convenient urban option.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I take my dog to the Whitewater Center?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"The U.S. National Whitewater Center is very dog-friendly, allowing leashed dogs on its extensive trail network. It’s a fantastic spot for active dogs and owners.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in Gaston County?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Gaston County requires dogs to be under physical restraint (leash) or under the direct control of a competent person when off the owner’s property.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Gastonia\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/new-york\">New York</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/seattle\">Seattle</a></div></div><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"header-right\"><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><a class=\"header-link header-link-primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/signup\">Sign up</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/login\">Log in</a><button class=\"menu-toggle\" ari