wer</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">1</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Safety</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">2<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">2</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Rules &amp; Etiquette</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Events &amp; Parties</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Training</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a sidebar-card support-card\"><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-label\">Explorers</p><h3 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Trail guide</h3><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Find the best routes for your dog’s fitness level.</p><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-actions\"><a href=\"/hiking\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Hiking Guide</a><a href=\"/cities\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a secondary\">Park Map</a></div><small style=\"display:block;margin-top:12px\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Adventure awaits just outside town.</small></div></aside><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-main\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-rail\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-eyebrow\">Popular right now</span><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Tap to jump to the full answer.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Where can I hike with my dog near Gastonia?</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Is there a dog park in Gastonia?</button></div></div><div role=\"list\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-accordion\"><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">01</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Where can I hike with my dog near Gastonia?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Crowders Mountain State Park is the jewel of the area.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Crowders Mountain State Park is the jewel of the area. The trails range from moderate to strenuous, offering incredible views. Dogs must be on a leash at all times.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Facilities &amp; Features</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">02</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Is there a dog park in Gastonia?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Yes, the Goat Island Park (in nearby Cramerton) and Lineberger Park offer great outdoor spaces.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Yes, the Goat Island Park (in nearby Cramerton) and Lineberger Park offer great outdoor spaces. Bradley Station Dog Park in downtown Gastonia is a convenient urban option.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Facilities &amp; Features</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">03</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Can I take my dog to the Whitewater Center?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">The U.S.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Planning Your Visit</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">The U.S. National Whitewater Center is very dog-friendly, allowing leashed dogs on its extensive trail network. It’s a fantastic spot for active dogs and owners.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Planning Your Visit</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">04</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">What are the leash laws in Gaston County?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Gaston County requires dogs to be under physical restraint (leash) or under the direct control of a competent person when off the owner’s property.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">legal</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Gaston County requires dogs to be under physical restraint (leash) or under the direct control of a competent person when off the owner’s property.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->legal</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></section></div></section><section id=\"related-resources\" class=\"related-resources-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Keep exploring</span><h2>More ways to plan</h2><p>Browse statewide guides, submit a listing, or connect with our team.</p></div><div class=\"resources-grid\"><a class=\"resource-card\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"resource-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-globe\"></i></div><h3>California overview</h3><p>See every city we cover plus statewide insights.</p><i class=\"bi bi-arrow-up-right\"></i></a><a class=\"res