\"Yes, the Goat Island Park (in nearby Cramerton) and Lineberger Park offer great outdoor spaces. Bradley Station Dog Park in downtown Gastonia is a convenient urban option.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Can I take my dog to the Whitewater Center?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"The U.S. National Whitewater Center is very dog-friendly, allowing leashed dogs on its extensive trail network. It’s a fantastic spot for active dogs and owners.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"What are the leash laws in Gaston County?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Gaston County requires dogs to be under physical restraint (leash) or under the direct control of a competent person when off the owner’s property.\\\"}}]}26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$2e\\\"}}]\\n27:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"itemListElement\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Home\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":2,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":3,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Gastonia\\\\\\\"}]}\\\"}}]\\n28:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L11\\\",null,{\\\"variant\\\":\\\"light\\\"}]\\n29:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"items\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-hero\\\",\\\"titl