ational Whitewater Center is very dog-friendly, allowing leashed dogs on its extensive trail network. It’s a fantastic spot for active dogs and owners.\",\"category\":\"planning\"},{\"question\":\"What are the leash laws in Gaston County?\",\"answer\":\"Gaston County requires dogs to be under physical restraint (leash) or under the direct control of a competent person when off the owner’s property.\",\"category\":\"legal\"}],\"supportCard\":{\"kicker\":\"Explorers\",\"title\":\"Trail guide\",\"description\":\"Find the best routes for your dog’s fitness level.\",\"primary\":{\"label\":\"Hiking Guide\",\"href\":\"/hiking\"},\"secondary\":{\"label\":\"Park Map\",\"href\":\"/cities\"},\"footnote\":\"Adventure awaits just outside town.\"}}]}]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"className\":\"related-resources-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Keep exploring\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"More ways to plan\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Browse statewide guides, submit a listing, or connect with our team.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resources-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"resource-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resource-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-globe\"}]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"California overview\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"See every city we cover plus statewide insights.\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-arrow-up-right\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"resource-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resource-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chat-dots\"}]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Ask the team\"}